ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: If they had more experience and were already doing ancestral state reconstruction I would recommend this class. Otherwise, I think the time could be spent better doing directed readings alone.
I would recommend this class to anyone who like to develop a critical sense of this emerging discipline.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It definitely showed me many of the concerns and problems with ancestral state reconstruction that are out there. I don't think I was far enough along in my research to gain much from it though.
